  abstract = {In this work, we focus on point cloud k-Nearest Neighbor (kNN) search, an important kernel for point clouds. We propose BitNN, a bit-serial architecture for point cloud kNN search. BitNN supports adaptive precision processing and unnecessary computing reduction, significantly improving the performance and power efficiency of kNN search. BitNN achieves up to 6.6x speedup and 3.6x power efficiency compared to a comparable sized architecture.},
